profile_positions.description:
Specific responsibilities:

-	Develops mockups and sets up templates for email campaigns. Coordinates and communicates rules and module details for same to all relevant partners;

-	Sets up requests, coordinates and communicates rules and module details for on-site campaigns including homepage, alleys, takeover screen, flyout ads, specials pages and various other web ads;

-	Utilizes in-house and third-party analytic tools, to prepare weekly and monthly reports on email and web campaign performance. Makes recommendations based on objective data analysis to improve same;

-	Educates internal partners on email and web marketing processes, systems and best practices;

-	Participates in cross-functional project team meetings to launch new marketing initiatives.
